Package com.android.interfaces

Interface Move<T,​V>

All Known Implementing Classes:
Car, Robot, Vehicle
public interface Move<T,​V>
this interface has two generics T and V three classes implement the Move interface Robot implements and specifies the generic type to be used class Robot implements Move<Cow,Zebra> Vehicle implements and uses it's own generics to supply a type class Vehicle<U,X> implements Move<U,X> Car implments but does not specify any type class Car implements Move
